				<td colspan="2"><span>Well, I know from readding other posts that the lev 56 song won;t do a mem wipe, but there is an AA ability we can get called fading memories which will wipe -you- from all mobs hate lists.  So many bards will gate a mob and then fade immediately.  This will work assuming you are the only one that has pissed the mob off so far<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
I can;t answer your questions about the DoTs though... but that is awsome about your damage.  I am a 55 bard, and I use selos drum of the march, and I can only put out 67 damage per tick (per dot of course).  You must have a nice drum<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
