				<td colspan="2"><span>Thank you both for the responses.  I appreciate the feedback.  A little update...
<br />
I'm a bone head.  I didn't update reeds spreadsheet after I dinged so it is in fact supposed to do the numbers it says.  Which is great.  
<br />

<br />
Thanks for the tips Pele.  I like the caster interrupt if they are already at bind.  I could see some handy uses for this.
<br />
I do like the Heraldic alot for the ac/hp/mana but it's lacking in stats.  I heard a rumor that we may be able to change dieties in LDoN, but that's been a rumor since after SoL I think.  But if it's true then yea, I'm going for Rallos.  
<br />

<br />
Your comments on the mezz are exactly what seems to be happening.  It seemed I could mezz the adds faster than the chanter but after he overwrote, they'd still break in the 18 sec.  I'll refrain from mezzing till the chanter drops.
